{"tid":1568821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.31 - 最接近的真相","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:00:17.000Z","uid":53666,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"143562400ac7b1241bd807a8e5503fe77ad57861","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"消防記招之後, 真相開始浮現。<br />\n首先中秋節(9月13號) 下午五點, 有防消FB呢張相:<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WbqnhXm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWbqnhXm.gif&h=22a502ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">消防FB出燈謎 疑揭831重大啟示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566443</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後, 下午11點38分有前線消防員FB爆料<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: gold;\">前線消防爆料 荔枝角站兩個昏迷不醒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566661</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先, 多謝還有良心嘅消防/救護肯企前一步。希望有更多人會效法。<br />\n我明白你哋一定面對緊極巨大嘅心理壓力, 以至人身安全上嘅威脅。 請知道, 只有你掌握嘅秘密被公開後, 反而令你更安全。而你嘅時間唔多, 請做好對自己嘅保護 (例如不自殺聲明 / 搵有公信力嘅傳媒)。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正題:</span></span><br />\n如果 8.31 當日係大陸人扮嘅黑警打死咗人<br />\n<br />\n成件事係宇宙級核彈。共產黨必定用盡所有方法去掩飾，就等如 8964 嘅天安門一樣， 要令全世界相信 831 太子站 沒有死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整合目擊者同傳媒嘅料,<br />\n當日在一名消防見習主任係唯一一個可以喺 3-4 月台數傷者人數, 喺一段長時間 (0015-0102) 內, 傷者人數維持6紅2黃2綠。直到最後採用警方說法, 只有3紅2黃2綠<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69992223_2965726293444700_6206325895607615488_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQl6pbq4J9Bn0JRlu_q0UFcYMjypCtgZQROiaTgGe_gJALlfo1QODjsxCQqZzq6EF7g&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ea27202e9080e4c7a3725290c9ef2c7d&amp;oe=5E058F8D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69992223_2965726293444700_6206325895607615488_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQl6pbq4J9Bn0JRlu_q0UFcYMjypCtgZQROiaTgGe_gJALlfo1QODjsxCQqZzq6EF7g%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dea27202e9080e4c7a3725290c9ef2c7d%26oe%3D5E058F8D&h=c630f40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70151248_2968818309802165_8247694521064751104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQnLmGoXfyssqI1e_Wl-Rzl_sQ3tGfIY2HTFi7ZgmFPJirAQnhkitBS6nzuyU5io2hY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=f13111ce779178d859928a40a1013d89&amp;oe=5E0D24D8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70151248_2968818309802165_8247694521064751104_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_oc%3DAQnLmGoXfyssqI1e_Wl-Rzl_sQ3tGfIY2HTFi7ZgmFPJirAQnhkitBS6nzuyU5io2hY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Df13111ce779178d859928a40a1013d89%26oe%3D5E0D24D8&h=1238542f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n睇返記錄, 消防局局長報告有2個Head injuries傷者, 佢哋亦最有可能係已死去嘅二位傷者 (嚴重傷者目睹有兩張空擔架床一直放在荔枝角站)。<br />\n<blockquote>【推】8.31嚴重傷者現身說法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567585</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設有兩名香港人不明不白死去, 佢哋嘅屋企人一定會出聲。政權機器一定係先發制人咁去毁滅証據(屍體) 同 用盡所有方法令到唔會有手尾。 所以, 呢個亦係點解太子站要封兩日嘅原因。<br />\n<blockquote>原來9.1 有手足入咗太子站, 亦見到站內有警察做緊嘢:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VsLmWZD7va4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVsLmWZD7va4&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=8a14a372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VsLmWZD7va4</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用盡所有方法, 包括:</span></span><br />\n一. 處理所有太子站內嘅CCTV (月台同售票層)<br />\n黨鐵一定唔會交出CCTV片段, <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋有無可能, 搵返太子站內所有店鋪嘅8.31-9.2 嘅CCTV片段??<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n二. 處理所有死者嘅connection , 滅佢哋聲<br />\n咁多日來嘅可以跳樓同屍體發現 (包括理大呢單) <br />\n<blockquote>POLY Z CORE 自殺事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553645</a></blockquote><br />\n佢哋可能係死者二人, 或者更大可能係, 佢哋都嘅朋友或家人。而極權兇手可以用你想像唔到嘅方法去令件事降溫, 當無事發生過:<br />\nthis: <blockquote>秀義樓跳樓「義士」真相及CCTV片段<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaxKmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaxKmS</a></blockquote><br />\nand this:<blockquote>【突發】 HKFP意外拍攝到太子站女死者朋友：死者父母要求取回屍體被軟禁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kKvwxvX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kKvwxvX</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望大家留心有無一啲認識嘅朋友/親人, 喺9月1日之後無再露面 (不論有無解釋)</span></strong><br />\n第一, 請你哋自己小心 (因為下個可能係你)<br />\n第二, 請你哋馬上搵可信任嘅傳媒 (Apple, 立場, HKFP) 同佢哋報料, 保持接解。<br />\n喺安全情況下, 和傳媒一起報警。<br />\n<strong>第三, 謹記千萬不要自己一個去報警</strong><br />\n<br />\n樓主利申: 本人十分幸福快樂, 身體健康, 精神爽利, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本人沒有任何理由會自殺。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n-完-"},{"pid":"975379fded2fce33c99a5ac6932068663558d52a","tid":1568821,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"399e62218f28eb870903f2d55eb6b45bc5c8fd34","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑警或其背後大佬, 會用盡所有方法令到死人呢件事唔會有手尾。</span>"},{"pid":"81dcbb6da098aa901e57c273b39279d3bfa17798","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本人沒有任何理由會自殺。</span><br />\n<br />\n請問:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仲有無可能, 搵返太子站內所有店鋪嘅8.31-9.2 嘅CCTV片段??<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"17bf5343bdb03ac7eaaf8c45fac37a05e96bc089","tid":1568821,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"[有文宣喺度] 休息過後，大家向前行多步<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaFjuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaFjuS</a>"},{"pid":"18132c5212ef383eb904879fb42dc41b8c38936a","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"雖然未必影到咩嘢, <br />\n但唔可以放過任何一個機會為死者嗚冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fd369e38dbccbe97890f35b25702e557c1dbdf","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AGxwLpDsIno/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAGxwLpDsIno%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=db85beef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f795dfa117825be258131cd39d8bfec6628a23","tid":1568821,"uid":291191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c63110a10d0e845487b8dcc5e1ca2a09227e50ee","tid":1568821,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hlG7gcryrM2gKHhh8jNFMPzBIMAc5ciBrbihia0lwbVxyKHY3ZXB1BikfZA8ge3Q2ZCp6ByYbKFl3fiNtNXF1/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hlG7gcryrM2gKHhh8jNFMPzBIMAc5ciBrbihia0lwbVxyKHY3ZXB1BikfZA8ge3Q2ZCp6ByYbKFl3fiNtNXF1%2Fw644&h=35f199c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>誓為死者嗚冤</strong></span>"},{"pid":"279e11cb6071fcb9315fe3c0a3b36bc5f7038f7c","tid":1568821,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"條片乜都影唔